Feature: Oneway Roundabout

    Background:
        Given the profile "testbot"

    Scenario: Simple Circle
        Given the node map
            |   |   | g |   |   |
            | a | b |   | d | f |
            |   |   | c |   |   |

        And the ways
            | nodes | oneway |
            | ab    | no     |
